This is a Play! framework bash completion script.

# USAGES #

  $ play [tab][tab]
  $ play help [tab][tab]
  
  will display the list of available play commands
  
  
  $ play run [tab][tab]
  
  will display the list of all play apps in the current directory (and subdirectories)


# HACKABILITY #

feel free to improve my script ;)
